{
  "texts": [
    "The study discovered that the photos generated by AI resembled real photographs.",
    "However, clinical accuracy varied between categories (the most correct images were soft-tissue tumors, whereas the most inaccurate ones accurate were wounds).",
    "Overall, the text-toimage AI technique is an emerging and promising tool in medical education.",
    "Diffusion models have revolutionized the field of medical image generation, enabling the creation of high-resolution synthetic images [89].",
    "Diffusion models, such as DDMM (Denoising Diffusion Medical Models) [90] and 3D-DDPM (Denoising Diffusion Probabilistic Models) [91,92], have shown great promise in producing high-resolution synthetic X-rays [90], MRIs, and CT images [92,93]."
  ]
}